{"tid":1415522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[現場目擊] 唔該，唔好再攞勇武屌7福建佬單野打飛機","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:12:56.000Z","uid":260946,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"127eb9f7ca5739e238ab011d648e7fc8e737a3e4","tid":1415522,"uid":260946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"利申：發完夢後撞到正，好彩已變身白衫打工仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一來：</strong><br />\n班友二打六，鐵通開山刀頭盔都冇 （有人話有菜刀，我係現場唔係好覺但係不能排除，need fc）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>二來，</strong><strong>好重要好重要</strong>：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實當時我哋大隊行得好散！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當初班佬叫囂嘅時候，大隊只得伶仃幾個冇gear、只有和理非口罩嘅手足；班手足之前仲叫緊口號，班佬叫囂即刻嚇到收晒聲急急腳過馬路。<strong>福建佬如果當時突襲，其實好危險</strong><br />\n<br />\n偏偏班傻仔叫囂成十分鐘先決定衝去打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時好彩叫得齊班殺龍巴絲佈陣，屌返佢哋轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝勇武手足，你哋好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">所以轉場嘅時候大家行得近少少，full gear同冇gear手足分布得平均啲，時刻照應對方</span></strong>；同埋隨時要有被突襲埋伏嘅戒備，唔可以鬆懈，尤其是而家對家越玩越過界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申：不分化，各有各做。只係親眼見到，擔心以後俾人埋伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef6659bc1659a6129429543300bcd9785d1867f","tid":1415522,"uid":260946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c481df37e224f61f60509275b1f03c61ca9501da","tid":1415522,"uid":194914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a63c6054446ddb94b09079aabb15a5411b6f6a0e","tid":1415522,"uid":260946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:56:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd4c7fd074af6a203758821dccddc1f689c52336","tid":1415522,"uid":190258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"行山杖真係好重要 希望各位手足都買返把 有咩事上嚟都可以還拖<br />\n如果今次唔係我地夠多人嘅話實會傷亡慘重"},{"pid":"53ed382615bd745a4638904de45b96b57aa59d10","tid":1415522,"uid":260946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4c7fd074af6a203758821dccddc1f689c52336","tid":1415522,"uid":190258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"行山杖真係好重要 希望各位手足都買返把 有咩事上嚟都可以還拖<br />\n如果今次唔係我地夠多人嘅話實會傷亡慘重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"全民行山杖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋真係唔好鬆懈，由其入深紅地區"},{"pid":"f6f61b6441c6bc72d0fca17a19414647788f36ad","tid":1415522,"uid":163997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"}]}